Koan Digital Game Design Document:


Dialogue Font Point 24/ IM FELL

Possible Cults:
Lilith(Vampires)
Fenrir(Werewolves)
Anubis(Undead)
Titania(Fey)
Chronos(Rare)(Wizards)
The Fool(Rare)(Rogues)

Cult Characteristics:
Lilith: Regenerates health. Quick. Low base health.
Fenrir: High base health. Deals heavy damage. Fights fair.
Anubis: Fights in hordes. Can resist death. Slow.
Titania: Utilizes status effects. Resistant to god tech. Deals low damage.

Level 1 Chests:
-1 Health Potion
-6 Revolver Bullets
-2 Keys
-Shotgun and Six Shells
-Part Of Artemis' Bow
-Grenade

Level 2 Chests:
-3 Health Potions
-Armor
-4 Keys
-Boots of Hermes
-Part of Artemisâ€™ Bow

Status Effects:
Dazed: 25% to the next attack to miss.
Burning: -1 HP each turn(ignores armor)
Chilled: Next attack deals half damage.

Rules:
Starting Ten Health
Starting 6 Bullets
Starting 2 Strength
Allies Have A Cooldown Of Three Rooms
5 Gauntlet Rooms Then A Boss

1 = First Floor
0 = Basement
2 = Second Floor
C = Cave
G = Hedge Maze
M = Quarry
E = Excavation Part 1

Room Outlines:

1A: Front Door
-Story: Establish The Soul Anathema
--Go Through A Window(Spend A Bullet)(1C)
--Use The Front Door(1D)

0A: Cellar Door
-Story: Establish Robert's Loyalty
--Enter The Cellar(0B)
--Enter The Cave(0C)

1B: Side Door
-Story: Establish Zeus
--Climb The Trellis(2A)
--Enter The Side Door(1E)

1C: Kitchen
-Threat: Cultist
-Reward: Two Keys
--Go To First Floor Gauntlet

1D: Entry Hall
-Reward: One Key
--Go To First Floor Gauntlet
--Go To Second Floor Gauntlet

0B: Cellar
-Clue: Dead Body Killed By Cultist
--Enter Basement Gauntlet

0C: Cave Entry
-Threat: Cultist
--Go To Cave Gauntlet

2A: Balcony
-Clue: See The Excavation Site
--Go To Second Floor Gauntlet

1E: Side Entry
-Reward/Threat: Random Minor Benefit Or Loss(Key/Bullets/Damage/Nothing)
--Go To First Floor Gauntlet

1F(Gauntlet): Temple Shrine
-Conditional: Unusable If You Have Any Dissent
-Reward: Blessing of The Gods
-Zeus: Gain The Smite Ability
-Ares: +2 Damage
-Asclepius: +4 Health
-Apollo: Learn A Random Secret
-Hermes: Gain Two Keys

1G(Gauntlet): Hallway
-Threat: Cultist

1H(Gauntlet): Corridor
-Reward: Locked Chest
-Reward: Locked Door

1I(Locked Door): Closet Of Asclepius
-Reward: 3 Health Potions

1J(Locked Door): Prison
-Reward: Random Disciple
-Zeus: Casts Smite
-Asclepius: Heal 3 Damage
-Hermes: Unlock An Object
-Aphrodite: Bonus To Negotiating
-Artemis: Find An Item

0D(Gauntlet): Dark Temple Shrine
-Reward: Dark Blessing(+1 Dissent)
-Lilith: Gain Lifesteal 1
-Fenrir: Gain Berserker Rage Ability
-Anubis: Gain Commune With Spirits Ability
-Titania: Gain Armor 1

0E(Gauntlet): Fountain
-Reward: Random Event
-Lose Half Your Life
-Fight A Water Demon
-Nothing
-Gain Excalibur
-Restore All Health
-Gain +1 Strength

0F(Gauntlet): Oracle
-Reward: Learn A Random Secret

0G(Gauntlet): Passageway
-Threat: Fight A Cultist

2B(Gauntlet): Long Hallway
-Threat: Fight Two Cultists

2C(Gauntlet): Heirloom Room
-Reward: A Large Chest

2D(Gauntlet): Decrepit Hallway
-Reward: Random Weapon
-50% Chance Of Damage
-Machine Gun
-Sniper
-Parrying Dagger

0H(Gauntlet): Shrine To The Fool
-Reward: Gain Luck(+1 Dissension)
-Lucky or Unlucky

1K(Gauntlet): Mysterious Stranger
-Reward: +2 Keys
-1 Strength

2E(Gauntlet): Merchant
-Reward: Trade Keys For Items

0I(Gauntlet): Trapped Room
-Reward: +2 Keys
-50% Chance Of Damage

2F(Gauntlet): Atrium
-Threat: Elite Cultist
-Reward: 2 Keys

1L(Gauntlet): Dusty Room
-Reward 1 Key

1M(Boss): Ritual Room
-Threat: Boss Cultist
--Go Upstairs
--Go To Mansion Grounds(GA)

1N(Boss): Arena
-Threat: Knight of Mephistopheles
--Go Upstairs
--Go To Mansion Grounds(GA)

1O(Gauntlet): Library
-Clue: Random World Fact

2F(Gauntlet): Painting Room
-Threat: Giant Rat
-Reward: Key

2G(Boss): Greenhouse
-Threat: Monstrous Hydra Plant
--Go To Tram

1P(Gauntlet): Mallory's Room
-Reward: Mallory Joins Party
-Mallory Reminiscences If Already In The Party

2H(Boss): Variable
-Threat: Cultist Avatar
--Go To Tram

2I(Gauntlet): Bathroom
-Reward: Double Locked Cabinet
-Treasure Chest But Can Get Triple Health Potions

0G(Boss): Pump Station
-Threat: Exiled Vigilante
--Go To Mine
--Go Upstairs

0H(Gauntlet): Graffiti Room
-Reward: Treasure Chest
-Must Know The Password

OI(Boss): Computer Room
-Threat: Golem
--Go To Mine
--Go Upstairs

CA: Cave Entry
-Threat: Cultist
--Go To Cave Gauntlet

CB(Gauntlet): Tunnel
-Threat: Elite Cultist

CC(Gauntlet): Gauntlet
-Threat: 50% to take damage
-Can Bypass With The Password

CD(Gauntlet): Hot Springs
-Reward: Heal or gain Strength

CE(Gauntlet): Locker Room
-Reward: Weapon or Bullets

CF(Gauntlet): Profane Shrine
-Threat: Elite Cultist Then Regular Cultist

CG(Boss): Warrior's Altar
-Threat: Corrupted Spirit
-Reward: Spear of Ares, 2 Keys
--Go To Basement

GA: Maze Entrance
-Reward: Merchant
--Go To Maze Gauntlet

GB(Gauntlet): Cultist Gathering
-Cult Specific Event

2J(Gauntlet): Display Room
-Reward: 2 Key or A Treasure Chest

GC(Gauntlet): Natural Pool
-Reward Gain Full Health
-Can Be Skipped

GD(Gauntlet): Crossway
-Threat: Minotaur
-Can Be Skipped With A Key

GE(Gauntlet): Straightway
-Reward: Gain Two Keys

GF(Gauntlet): Culdesac
-Reward: Level 2 Treasure
-50% To Take Damage

GG(Gauntlet): Hermit's Hut
-Reward: Learn A Fighting Style

GH(Gauntlet): Traveling Merchant
-Reward: Merchant

GI(Gauntlet): Center Of The Maze
-Reward: Gain A Homing Beacon

GJ(Gauntlet): Clearing
-Reward: Either A Seraph Or A Repentant Cultist

GK(Gauntlet): Mausoleum
-Reward: Level 1 Treasure Chest And Level 3 Treasure Chest
-Costs 1 and 3 Keys

0J(Gauntlet): Basement Elevator
-Reward: Switch Floors

2K(Gauntlet): 2nd Floor Elevator
-Reward Switch Floors

GL(Boss): Maze's End
-Threat: Cult Siege Engine
-Can Be Avoided If Maze Base Is Lost
--Return To Maze
--Go To Upper Excavation Site

GM(Boss): Variable
-Threat: Cultist God
-Can Join The Cult
--Return To Maze
---Go To Upper Excavation Site

MA: Mine Entrance
-Choose Between Playing As Alison Or Robert
--Go To Mine Gauntlet

MB(Gauntlet): Soothsayer
-Story: Reveal Alison's Secret

MC(Gauntlet): Ancient Study
-Reward: Gain Mallory
-Mallory Story Scene If She Is Already In The Party

MD(Gauntlet): Fetid Pool
-Threat: Elite Cultist




ME(Gauntlet): Mine Car
-Reward: Reunite Party
-Requires Two Keys
--Go To Mine Boss Fight

MF(Gauntlet): Traveling Merchant
-Reward: Merchant

MG(Gauntlet): Tunnel
-Threat: Two Elites
-Reward: Level 3 Treasure
-Can Be Skipped

MH(Gauntlet): Variable
-Character Specific Encounter

MI(Gauntlet End): Laboratory
-Characters Rejoined
-Story Moment, Depends On What The Character Learned In The Gauntlet

MJ(Boss): Laboratory
-Threat: Alison
-Only If Robert Learned Alison's Secret And Chooses To Fight Her
--Go To Upper Excavation Site

MK(Boss): Quarry
-Threat: Earth Elemental
--Go To Upper Excavation Site

ML(Boss): Quarry
-Threat: Seraphim Swarm
-Only Triggers If The Players Have Dissension
--Go To Upper Excavation Site

MN(Boss): Quarry
-Threat: The High Priest
--Go To Upper Excavation Site

TA: Tram
-Threat: Demon
-Reward: Level 2 Treasure Chest
--Go To Upper Excavation Site

EA: Excavation Entrance
-Threat: Demon
-Must Encounter Whenever Coming From The Maze
--Go To Upper Excavation Gauntlet


EB(Gauntlet): Power Room
-Reward: Power
-Requires Two Keys

GN(Gauntlet): Forest
-Reward: Wood Production
-Requires: A Base
-Will Stay In Pool Until Tagged

GO(Gauntlet): Abandoned Camp
-Reward: Turrets

EC(Gauntlet): Observation Room
-Threat: Dark Priest
-Reward: Two Keys
-Will Keep Appearing Until Station Is Powered

ED(Gauntlet): Forge
